title: US Financial, Political Elites Firmly Wedded to House of Saud
text: US President Obama supports the ruthless Saudi leadership, at the same time placing the blame for the deaths of tens of thousands on the secular government of Bashar al-Assad in Syria, US author Eric Zuesse noted, adding that Washington's foreign policy is currently controlled by an aristocracy that's firmly wedded to the House of Saud. ...
